title: Crystal Glass Nail File Set , 5.5" File and 3.5" File, Free Carrying Case From Sassella
description: This Crystal Nail File Set, includes one 5.5" and one 3.5" file. The 5.5" file has a delicate hand-painted flower. These elegant crystal files are unlike ordinary nail files that create tiny fractures in your nail which can weaken the nail and cause the nail to split and become brittle. Because the glass file is so hard and the filing surface so extremely fine, you can file in any direction without damaging the nail. It will leave your nails incredibly smooth! Amazingly the glass file works very well on extremely hard nails as well as very soft nails. Since the surface of the glass nail file is so fine and uniform, regular use will actually help grow more beautiful nails, they will be healthier and smoother.
